The wallet's script is encoded as a tree of operators rooted at the top-level descriptor wrapper. Each operator is identified by a single tag byte. The tag table below adopts the assignments used by <code>descriptor-codec</code> (CC0-1.0) for full miniscript compatibility, with MD-specific extensions for BIP 388 wallet-policy semantics.

